<section class="container-fluid bg-color3 d-flex flex-column py-20">
  <h1 class="text-center">How it works</h1>
  <div class="d-flex flex-row justify-content-around flex-wrap">
    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center m-15 card-small">
      <div><%= image_tag("sliders.svg", style: "height:100px; width:auto") %></div>
      <h2 class="color-dark">Pilot Preferences</h2>
      <p class="text-center lh-base">
      <b class="color-primary">Your way of flying, your rules.</b> Set your weather aversion level, min runway length, and other rules to expect tailor made results. All destinations we'll suggest you will fit your preferences.
      </p>
      <p class="text-center">
        <%= link_to "Read more",
          root_path,
          class: "btn btn-dark",
          style: "font-size: 1em;",
          onclick: "event.preventDefault();" %>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center m-15 card-small">
      <div><%= image_tag("briefcase.svg", style: "height:100px; width:auto") %></div>
      <h2 class="color-dark">Find Destinations</h2>
      <p class="text-center lh-base"><b class="color-primary">Time is valuable.</b> Just want a lunch, or to leave the weekend, maybe even longer, just tell us what you expect to find at destination.In a few clicks, you'll discover our best destinations. And <b class="color-primary">only where weather is welcoming you!</b></p>
      <p class="text-center">
        <%= link_to "Read more",
          root_path,
          class: "btn btn-dark",
          style: "font-size: 1em;",
          onclick: "event.preventDefault();" %>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center m-15 card-small">
      <div><%= image_tag("message-circle.svg", style: "height:100px; width:auto") %></div>
      <h2 class="color-dark">Community</h2>
      <p class="text-center lh-base">
      <b class="color-primary">Pilots only trust pilots.</b><br>Share your experiences, rate places, follow insipring pilots, share usefull information to the community. Benefit from your community.
      </p>
      <p class="text-center">
        <%= link_to "Read more",
          root_path,
          class: "btn btn-dark",
          style: "font-size: 1em;",
          onclick: "event.preventDefault();" %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag('paper_plane.svg', style: "width:200px;position: relative;
bottom: -50px;left: 50px") %>
</section>
